## ConStatic MongoDB Module API Reference

```APIDOC
ConStaticMongoDB:
  __init__(connection_string: str, db_name: str)
    connection_string: The MongoDB connection URI.
    db_name: The name of the database to connect to.

  connect() -> Promise<Database>
    Establishes a connection to MongoDB.
    Returns: A Promise that resolves to the connected database instance.
    Throws: Error if connection fails.

  collection(collection_name: str) -> Collection
    Retrieves a specific collection instance.
    collection_name: The name of the collection.
    Returns: A MongoDB Collection object.

  insert(collection_name: str, document: object) -> Promise<InsertOneResult>
    Inserts a single document into a collection.
    collection_name: The target collection.
    document: The document to insert.
    Returns: A Promise resolving to the insert result.

  find(collection_name: str, query: object = {}) -> Promise<Array<object>>
    Finds documents in a collection.
    collection_name: The target collection.
    query: Optional. A query object to filter results. Defaults to empty (all documents).
    Returns: A Promise resolving to an array of matching documents.
```

